.TH SHOAL-LANDLOCK-HELPER 1 "July 2026" "Shoal 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
shoal-landlock-helper \- probe Shoal Landlock enforcement
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B shoal-landlock-helper
.I allowed_path denied_path
.SH DESCRIPTION
Internal installation diagnostic that verifies an allowed path remains readable while a denied path does not.
Its exit status is intended for Shoal Doctor rather than interactive use.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR shoal-doctor (1),
.BR shoal-sandbox-exec (1)
